name: EXES FOR EYES - Amsler Grid Limited Edition Package
description:
EXES FOR EYES debut with "The Amsler Grid," 9 killer tracks of uncompromising metallic rock n' roll. Featuring Big James from Endast and Dave Sheldon from Man With Target, EXES FOR EYES bring it in an honest way. Pick up the limited edition package today.


Package Includes:

1 CD Copy of "The Amsler Grid"
1 Limited Edition Album T-shirt

*** All packages are shipped 1-3 days after confirmation of purchase.

name: NORRIS - Great White North Limited Edition Package

name: NORRIS - The Great White North
description:
The hotly anticipated new full length record from Thunder Bay's Norris is finally here. A crushing assault on the senses, "The Great White North" just became your new must have record of 2011.

For Fans Of: Converge, The Red Chord, Gaza, and The Dillinger Escape Plan.


1. The Great White North
2. De-Evolution of Music
3. Economics without Ecology
4. The Dregs
5. Peasant
6. Jesus Heist
7. Food for Thought
8. Plaything the Role
9. Chump Change

name: EXES FOR EYES - The Amsler Grid
description:
Featuring Big James (Endast) and Dave Sheldon (Man With Target), Exes For Eyes debut with their first full length album entitled "The Amsler Grid." A tight combination of metallic grooves and classic rock archetypes, Exes For Eyes are a fresh band with trusted influences. 


1. Feel Again
2. A Life so Unfulfilling
3. Exes for Eyes
4. Romanticize the Struggle
5. Stop Thinking, Start Feeling
6. Embrace the Fire
7. Chains
8. Dig for Higher Ground
9. A Horrible Mistake

*** Album ships before the release date of April 26, 2011 ***

5. At the Bottom
